\noindent To the Editor,

\vspace{11pt}
We are pleased to submit a Data Descriptor manuscript entitled ``A spatio-temporal land use/land cover reconstruction for India (1960--2010)'' for consideration for publication in \textit{Scientific Data}. The manuscript describes a new, high-resolution historical land use/land cover dataset for India, produced by combining contemporary land use/land cover maps derived from satellite data with subnational inventory data. The data has been placed in the Figshare repository (doi TODO). \\

\vspace{11pt}
The manuscript has not been published and is not under consideration for publication elsewhere. We have previously submitted a draft abstract of the manuscript to a member of your Editorial Board, Katherine Homewood, to register our interest in participating in a special collection dedicated to the Ecosystem Services for Poverty Alleviation (ESPA) project. We have identified the following potential reviewers for the manuscript:

\vspace{11pt}
\begin{enumerate}
\item Dr Richard Fuchs (Karlsruhe Institute of Technology, richard.fuchs@kit.edu)
\item Dr Arijit Roy (Indian Institute of Remote Sensing, arijitroy@iirs.gov.in)
\end{enumerate}

